author: National Geographic
description:
A penguin scientist makes an astonishing discovery: interspecies mating between a Macaroni Penguin and a Rockhopper Penguin. This is an incredibly rare sighting in the wild, defying typical penguin behavior. What brought the two penguins together?

author: National Geographic
description:
Mozzarella stretching, sausage stuffing, and a ceiling full of meat! Jo Franco is discovering what makes New York’s Little Italy so authentic. But this isn’t Manhattan, Jo’s heading to the Bronx’s Arthur Avenue for the challenge. In this neighborhood scavenger hunt, she meets the butchers, bakers, and pasta makers keeping Italian traditions alive. Along the way, she tastes her way through family-run institutions and uncovers what makes this Little Italy the real deal.

For more yummy Italian food, check out Tucci In Italy, now streaming on @disneyplus and @hulu: http://di.sn/6009NqAgH
